{
  "id": "adv_main_01_09_06",
  "title": "星見編2章31話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_way-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "（小さい頃から、お姉ちゃんがいつも近くにいた）\n（変わらないでほしい日常、だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ever since we were little‚ my big sister was always by my side.)\n(I wished those days would never change.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.866666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、本当は……）\n（変わらなきゃいけないとも、思っていたんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But‚ the truth is…)\n(Something had to change. And I knew it.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-multi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9233.333333333334,
          "startTime": 22.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-3d",
      "startTime": 17.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 18.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-com001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……なんか、気持ちいいね！\n朝の浜辺走るの、私好きかもっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* This just feels so good‚ huh!\nA morning jog by the shore… I think I like it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-com003.m4a",
      "text": "うー……芽衣は朝苦手かも……\n……つらいよー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Urrrgh… I think I hate mornings.\nThis sucks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-com002.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ……練習量増やそうって話は\nみんなで決めたことなんだし……頑張ろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now‚ we decided to train more.\nIt was a decision we reached together… So hang in there‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "今さら文句を言ったって、グランプリのエントリー\nもう済ませてるんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s too late to complain now. The Grand Prix…\nwe’ve already put in our application.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-com004.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ後戻りなんてできない……\nここから先は弱肉強食の世界、気は抜けませんわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no turning back now.\nFrom this point forth‚ it’s survival of the fittest. We mustn’t lose an ounce of vigor!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんのは\nちょっと気合い入り過ぎ……な気もするけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In your case‚ Suzu…\nI think you’ve got too much vigor… Just a feeling I have.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、無駄話多過ぎ\n喋りながら走ってると、すぐ息切れするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Girls‚ you’re talking too much.\nIf you talk while running‚ you’ll quickly run out of breath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "呼吸を意識して走るのも大事なんだから\n集中、集中っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s important to focus on your breathing while you run.\nFocus! Focus!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "は～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-multi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.3333333333344,
          "startTime": 79.13333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 79.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ぜぇ……はあ……ぜぇ……はあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*wheeze* *huff* *wheeze* *huff*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫……はぁ、はぁ……だから\n雫ちゃん、先、行ってて……いいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m o-okay… *huff* *huff* So‚\nShizuku… go on… ahead… of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃんも……\n心配、しないで……大丈夫、だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you too‚ Saki.\nDon’t worry… about me. I’ll be… okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "そう……分かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……無理、しないでね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please… don’t hurt yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（……体力、もっとつけないと）\n（どんどん、みんなの……足手まといになっちゃう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I need… to increase my stamina.)\n(Otherwise… I’ll gradually become… a burden to everyone.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……あ、あれ？\nお、お姉ちゃん……待っててくれたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* Huh?\nS-Saki? You waited for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.03333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "……放っておけなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I couldn’t just leave you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……みんな、先に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… the others went ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "焦らなくても大丈夫よ、千紗\nだから……一緒に走りましょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to stress over this‚ Chisa.\nSo… why don’t we run together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "……うん\nお姉ちゃん……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.\nSaki… Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "04-2d",
      "startTime": 146.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 146.83333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "（放課後、雫ちゃんと合流してレッスンに向かう）\n（それが、私達の日課になっていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After school‚ I meet up with Shizuku to go to our lessons.)\n(It’s become a daily routine for us.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "04-2d",
      "startTime": 155.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "……はあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "04-2d",
      "startTime": 158.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、ため息……ダメ\n幸せ、逃げちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa. You’re sighing. Don’t.\nYour happiness will escape.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "04-2d",
      "startTime": 164.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_06-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "そう、だよね\nちょっと考えごとしてたら……つい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you’re right.\nI just had something on my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
